name: Bolot HomeStay Banyumala
address: Wanagiri, Sukasada, Buleleng Regency, Bali 81161, Indonesia
review 1:
This is the most wonderful place that I had stayed 4 days with nature and got experiences about local family, traditional small village...many beautiful waterfall arround this homestay.The ower and his family treated me so kind, we spent time together talk in the evening, cooked together, the ower showed me his village and invited me join his family ceremonies...his wife and kids are also cute.I love all things here and 100% will come back to visist them again one day üòä
...Guys, if you are in Bali, you must try this homestay to get 100% different experience maybe you have ever tried.
Lyn from Vietnam had been here on 3/9/2019 - 6/9 2019
review 2: I had Stay with in bolot homestay for a few days,and i had more experience about the nature,and bolot is so nice host, so we had more experience about the nature from him,and just take 5 minuts from huge waterfall from his house ,so it's like incredible ,,,,,,  so anyone intrested with new experience about the nature ,just come and stay with him,,
review 3: Good place to stay.very close to waterfall,,,
review 4: Stay here.feel like in my own house..
